cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.RO

The paper deals with the analysis and verification of neural network-based controllers for cyber-physical systems, which involves topics related to control theory, machine learning, and robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper also involves numerical methods for solving differential equations, which falls under cs.NE (Numerical Analysis) and the application of the approach to robotics, which falls under cs.RO (Robotics).
